{
  "stem": "9478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had with me 88,000 rubles-- 44,000 rubles in one boot and 44,000 rubles in another boot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took Sonia on the market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the market, you can get anything-- anything what you have desires.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the price was very, very high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I dressed her complete.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't come with anything in my mind, you know, that I'll marry her or sex, or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because that time, was nothing in the mind, but just to help somebody out-- especially I knew she was a delicate person at home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to school together for a few years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I says, do you want to stay here, or do you want to come with me to Chelyabinsk?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do not want that people should think that I came to use her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, well, OK, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon as I came to Chelyabinsk, right away they call me to the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I changed my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, it was luck too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them they let through, and some of them they took to the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a disorder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyways, I got-- what they call this thing-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called me to the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here is Sonia with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took away from the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I changed my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ran away with Sonia back to Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did you manage to change your name?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just told them that my name is Konstantinowsky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but you needed papers for--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What can papers?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What papers?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They believed-- papers, I destroyed the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't a order like now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in Russia, everybody was supposed to have an identity, otherwise--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I destroyed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I destroyed my license and my passport when I left home too.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
